1. *Tišina* je najglađa muzika. (Silence is the smoothest music.) 
2. Osećam *tišinu* u sobi. (I feel the silence in the room.) 
3. *Tišinom* se čuje najglađa muzika. (The smoothest music is heard in silence.) 
4. Grad je bio prekriven *tišinom*. (The city was covered in silence.) 
5. *Tišinu* smo razbili sa našim smehom. (We broke the silence with our laughter.) 
6. U *tišini* su se osećali njeni strahovi. (Her fears were felt in the silence.)